{"tid":730164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"慶祝獨立242年   美海軍最老護衛艦「憲法號」今出航","createTime":"2018-07-05T07:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T02:16:00.000Z","uid":184679,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8d79af2dae252907707c37f9f72c074835c1753a","tid":730164,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T07:35:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-07-05/656/20180705001551.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-07-05%2F656%2F20180705001551.jpg&h=f4490222&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">從1797年下水服役、至今仍是美軍艦隊一員的憲法號護衛艦。（圖/美國海軍）</span><br />\n<br />\n據美國波士頓環球報（Boston globe）報導，美國當地今日（7/4）迎來獨立日（Independence Day），各城市和機關無不舉辦特別活動，慶祝美國獨立242週年。在波士頓港（Boston Harbor）邊，有一艘具有歷史意義、也是美國現役「最老」的護衛艦憲法號（USS Constitution），載滿遊客和工作人員，在21槍響禮遇下，駛出港口以紀念獨立日。<br />\n<br />\n1797年下水服役的憲法號護衛艦，是美國創立之初建造的首批軍艦之一，曾參與美法準戰爭、第一次巴巴里戰爭與1812年美英戰爭（War of 1812）等多場戰役，保護遭受私掠的美國商船，並且立下顯赫戰功，更因為在戰爭中未受到嚴重傷害，被外界暱稱為「老鐵殼」（Old Ironsides）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-07-05/656/20180705001518.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-07-05%2F656%2F20180705001518.jpg&h=b6ea4805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">美國海軍憲法號護衛艦，於1812年與英軍交戰的繪畫。（圖/美國國家公園管理處）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/Bk0ZksDhZ38/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBk0ZksDhZ38%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&h=1e18eb59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n憲法號曾派駐地中海與太平洋地區，並在1844年進行環球旅行，耗時兩年的時間，先後到訪里約熱內盧、馬達加斯加、莫三比克、辛巴威、蘇門答臘、新加坡、峴港、廣州、馬尼拉、檀香山、馬薩特蘭等港口，最終返回波士頓。於1881年退役，曾因為船體老舊朽壞，美國政府曾考慮要轉作靶艦擊沉，但遭到輿論大力反彈。經過多次籌資募款，1925年進廠全面翻修、1931年重新服役至今。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-07-05/656/20180705001529.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-07-05%2F656%2F20180705001529.jpg&h=43cd745e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">憲法號上，穿著18、19世紀船長服裝的指揮官，頒發證書給協助出航的美軍水手。（圖/USS Constitution臉書專頁）</span><br />\n<br />\n聯絡官史庫勒下士（Casey Scoular）表示，為慶祝美國獨立日，今日搭乘憲法號的旅客，一趟約可乘載400多位，可在船上能聽到朗誦版的《獨立宣言》（Declaration of Independence）、體驗當年長槍與火砲填裝與射擊的實況，真實感受當年18世紀的美國生活。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180705001501-260417\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180705001501-260417&d=bKO%2BRaOqStztDnSgQgnBHzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=5ab2e63c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180705001501-260417</a>"},{"pid":"823a2a36a4114082662ba352be8bdc614e5bbfd9","tid":730164,"uid":51701,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T07:39:53.000Z","msg":"我地中國都有隻二戰蘇聯改裝艦仲用緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd4d2d955b512ae6fe73905acf138d83da12d6b","tid":730164,"uid":43721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T07:53:21.000Z","msg":"好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"334705631bf2221b7d586ea6d4b0caac89e9f4e5","tid":730164,"uid":39012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T07:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6133f2c73be1001215de7a6fc21489376e55df8","tid":730164,"uid":154872,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T08:05:13.000Z","msg":"屌, 諗起fallout"},{"pid":"2d784370deb60443579e86d33c613856ed11a5c8","tid":730164,"uid":59832,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d6133f2c73be1001215de7a6fc21489376e55df8","ti